org.osmdroid.bonuspack.kml
Interface KmlFeature.Styler

Enclosing class:
KmlFeature
public static interface KmlFeature.Styler

When building Overlays, a custom Styler can be defined to perform specific actions on specific objects. Each method is called just after Overlay creation. If a Styler is defined, no styling is applied by default. Note that an applyDefaultStyling method is available, to perform default styling if needed.
